\begin_layout Standard
At EcoNum, we use scientific devices connected to computers as much as possible.
 On one hand, it allows great flexibility in automatizing even complex tasks
 by writing computer programs to pilot the scientific devices, and in the
 other hand, it is fast and reliable to collect data from instruments directly
 into the computer as much as possible.
 When you take note of your measurements, then introduce them manually in
 the computer, you waste your time, but there is also a possibility to make
 mistakes when you copy the data.
\end_layout

